        "intro_content": "<p>The <strong>Xinzuo Lan Series (B37)</strong> is “The Pro” — the pinnacle of the Xinzuo range. Forged with a proprietary <strong>14Cr14MoVNb powder steel</strong> core wrapped in 73 layers of Damascus steel, the Lan delivers exceptional edge retention at HRC 62. This is the same construction that earned a Silver Award at the 2023 Commercial Kitchen Innovation Challenge. Olive wood handles add warmth and character to each blade. The powder steel core holds its edge significantly longer than standard 10Cr15CoMoV, making it the top choice for professional chefs and serious home cooks who demand the absolute best. If you want one series that represents the peak of Xinzuo’s craft, this is it.</p>",
